N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 3 ยง 300.4 - Other reports

State Regulations

Reports shall also be made of any other incident if there
are indications that it, or any act therein involved, relates to a plan or
scheme and would be of interest to similar organizations located in the same
area or throughout the State. Notes
